Class AbstractCubeHttpHandler

  • java.lang.Object
    • co.cask.cdap.internal.api.AbstractProgramDatasetConfigurable

        • co.cask.cdap.api.service.http.AbstractHttpServiceHandler
          • co.cask.cdap.api.dataset.lib.cube.AbstractCubeHttpHandler
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    HttpServiceHandler

    @Beta
public abstract class AbstractCubeHttpHandler
extends AbstractHttpServiceHandler
    A basic implementation of HttpServiceHandler that provides endpoints to explore and execute queries in Cube dataset.

    Subclasses must implement getCube() that returns Cube dataset.
